al.com/blog/obama_meeting&quot;&gt;What I think Obama is meeting with Jobs, Schmidt, and Zuckerberg about&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;Obama is meeting with a few technology leaders today.  Here's what I think they're talking about. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://theoatmeal.com/blog/obama_meeting&quot;&gt;View&lt;/a&gt;</description>\n    </item>\n    <item rdf:about=\"http://theoatmeal.com/blog/free_poster\">\n        <dc:format>text/html</dc:format>\n        <dc:date>2011-02-16T15:20:15+01:00</dc:date>\n        <dc:source>http://theoatmeal.com</dc:source>\n        <dc:creator>Matthew Inman</dc:creator>\n        <title>Buy any poster and get a free coffee poster</title>\n        <link>http://theoatmeal.com/blog/free_poster</link>\n        <description>&lt;a href=&quot;http://theoatmeal.com/blog/free_poster&quot;&gt;Buy any poster and get a free coffee poster&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;Buy one poster get a free copy of 15 things worth knowing about coffee.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://theoatmeal.com/blog/free_poster&quot;&gt;View&lt;/a&gt;</description>\n    </item>\n    <item rdf:about=\"http://theoatmeal.com/blog/valentines_day\">\n        <dc:format>text/html</dc:format>\n        <dc:date>2011-02-14T10:44:36+01:00</dc:date>\n        <dc:source>http://theoatmeal.com</dc:source>\n        <dc:creator>Matthew Inman</dc:creator>\n        <title>The worst thing about Valentine's Day</title>\n        <link>http://theoatmeal.com/blog/valentines_day</link>\n        <description>&lt;a href=&quot;http://theoatmeal.com/blog/valentines_day&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://s3.amazonaws.com/theoatmeal-img/thumbnails/valentines_day.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;A short rant on everyone's least favorite holiday.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://theoatmeal.com/blog/valentines_day&quot;&gt;View&lt;/a&gt;</description>\n    </item>\n    <item rdf:about=\"http://theoatmeal.com/comics/restaurant_website\">\n        <dc:format>text/html</dc:format>\n        <dc:date>2011-02-08