n of their site is romanced with magical oats. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://theoatmeal.com/blog/digg_tab&quot;&gt;View&lt;/a&gt;</description>\n    </item>\n    <item rdf:about=\"http://theoatmeal.com/blog/fail_whale\">\n        <dc:format>text/html</dc:format>\n        <dc:date>2011-01-31T14:09:32+01:00</dc:date>\n        <dc:source>http://theoatmeal.com</dc:source>\n        <dc:creator>Matthew Inman</dc:creator>\n        <title>A nice day at the beach with the Fail Whale and some Tumbeasts</title>\n        <link>http://theoatmeal.com/blog/fail_whale</link>\n        <description>&lt;a href=&quot;http://theoatmeal.com/blog/fail_whale&quot;&gt;A nice day at the beach with the Fail Whale and some Tumbeasts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;I drew Tumblr's new mascot spending some quality time at the beach with the Fail Whale.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://theoatmeal.com/blog/fail_whale&quot;&gt;View&lt;/a&gt;</description>\n    </item>\n    <item rdf:about=\"http://theoatmeal.com/comics/state_web_winter\">\n        <dc:format>text/html</dc:format>\n        <dc:date>2011-01-24T10:31:13+01:00</dc:date>\n        <dc:source>http://theoatmeal.com</dc:source>\n        <dc:creator>Matthew Inman</dc:creator>\n        <title>This is the web right now</title>\n        <link>http://theoatmeal.com/comics/state_web_winter</link>\n        <description>&lt;a href=&quot;http://theoatmeal.com/comics/state_web_winter&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://s3.amazonaws.com/theoatmeal-img/thumbnails/state_web_winter.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;The state of the web for Winter 2010. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://theoatmeal.com/comics/state_web_winter&quot;&gt;View&lt;/a&gt;</description>\n    </item>\n    <item rdf:about=\"http://theoatmeal.com/book_tour\">\n        <dc:format>text/html</dc:format>\n        <dc:date>2011-01-23T13:35:20+01:00</dc:date>\n        <dc:source>http://theoatmeal.com</dc:source>\n        <dc:creator>Matthew Inman</dc:creator>\n        <title>The Oatm